long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Fashion searcher is a new tab Chrome extension that helps you quickly search for the best fashion websites on the web

Disclaimer:
Fashion searcher will change your New Tab search results to be Powered by Microsoft Bing. The extensions will not make any changes to any other search setting in your browser

Note, By installing the Fashion searcher extension,  you agree to the Terms of Service and the Privacy Policy as follows:

Privacy Policy: https://fashion-searcher.com/privacy-policy/
Terms of Service: https://fashion-searcher.com/terms-of-service/
